---
title: Chorizo Queso Fundido Pizzettes with Cilantro and Roasted Red Peppers
description: We've taken the classic flavours of chorizo queso fundido and slapped them on a pizza! Rich, gooey Monterey Jack and cream cheese are spread onto crispy pitas and topped off with fresh cilantro and roasted peppers. It's a combo you didn't realize you were missing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mini-pizzas-style-queso-fundido-au-chorizo-3fe37358.jpg
